summary: “You might not be able to fight like a samurai, but you can at least die like a samurai.“ I was practicing a concept that I've...
caption:
“You might not be able to fight like a samurai, but you can at least die like a samurai.“

I was practicing a concept that I’ve done before with people and flower meanings. I decided to do a painting of O-Ren Ishii played by Lucy Liu and pairing her with Tsubaki or Camellias which means Humility. I just thought it suited her when she met her end.

Time est.: 6 hours

This is for my digital illustration class :D
